title: Susan Pearose, PA-C Named Top Dermatology Physician Assistant in Newport Beach

content.content: Susan Pearose, PA-C has been recognized as one of the top dermatology physician assistants in Newport Beach, a testament to her exceptional skills and dedication to patient care.
